                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-228-off1260 t18300415-228-cd1261"></join>, 1 silver mug, value 5l., and 1 cruet-stand, value 2l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-228-victim2000" type="victimName">
