                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-228-victim2000 t18300415-228-viclabel1263"></join>. This is my property; I valued them together at 5l. at Hatton-garden.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY (of stealing to the value of 99s. only.) Aged. 13.</p>
